* get order number from first delivery line item
CLEAR GS_IT_REFORD.

DATA: LS_REFORD LIKE LINE OF IS_DLV_DELNOTE-IT_REFORD.

READ TABLE IS_DLV_DELNOTE-IT_REFORD INTO GS_IT_REFORD INDEX 1.
IF SY-SUBRC NE 0.
CLEAR GS_IT_REFORD.
ELSE.
LOOP AT IS_DLV_DELNOTE-IT_REFORD INTO LS_REFORD
WHERE NOT ORDER_NUMB IS INITIAL.
IF GS_IT_REFORD-ORDER_NUMB NE LS_REFORD-ORDER_NUMB.
*    non unique order numbers in delivery
CLEAR GS_IT_REFORD.
EXIT.
ENDIF.
ENDLOOP.
ENDIF.























